          ul.posts
            li.post
              h1 Wrecka Stow Record Store <br><br>
                a(href="http://possiblegazer-wreckastow.herokuapp.com") Live link to Wrecka Stow
              p Wrecka Stow is a simple content management system that allows users to add, delete, or update [records] books. Books entered in the system can be viewed in a listing, or searched for using basic searches (title, author, genre). This project was a play on a bookstore but using records/musicians that are relevant to the aesthetic we were going for when creating this project. Here's a link to the Github repo: https://github.com/breyana/possible-gazer-bookstore
              img.portoneimage(src="http://i66.tinypic.com/35i0fiv.png")
              img.portoneimage(src="http://i68.tinypic.com/1zyg3fs.png")
              img.portoneimage(src="http://i67.tinypic.com/vfzi1e.png")
