                a(href="https://text-a-bae-app.herokuapp.com/views/index.html") Live link to Text A Bae
              p Text a bae is a program where you can send SMS messages via the web browser Here's a link to the Github repo: https://github.com/GeneralMeow/textABaeApp
              img.portoneimage(src="http://i63.tinypic.com/2rqn5lg.png")
            li.post
              h1.headerspace Open Source Software Contributions
                li.post
                  h2 Ancient Beasts
                    p Ancient Beast is a turn based strategy indie game project, played online against other people, featuring a wide variety of creatures to acquire and items to equip onto, putting them to use in order to defeat your opponents. This project was carefully designed to be easy to learn, fun to play and hard to master.
                  img.portoneimage(src="http://i65.tinypic.com/23lb2fq.png")
